criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Over 21 years of age;

          2. Without any chronic pathology;

          3. Score on the Spielberg Trait-State Anxiety Inventory (STAI-S) comprising 20 items,
             greater than 40 (probable clinical levels of anxiety);

          4. Pittsburgh Sleep Quality Index (PSQI) score greater than 5 (poor sleep quality).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Failure to meet the inclusion criteria.
